title: Drawing, "Female Head, Looking Right"
description: In the present drawing of a female turning right, the large, wide open eyes and full, slightly parted lips, and high cheekbones are the salient features. The face is framed by what appears to be a shoulder-length headdress or, perhaps, straight shoulder-length hair.

tombstone.epitaph:
Drawing, "Female Head, Looking Right".
19.8 x 14.5 cm (7 3/4 x 5 3/4 in.). Gift of Ellen Gustav Jensen. 1956-47-92.
